Description_lang: Increases Armor by ${$s1}.1% of your Agility. Armor bonus is doubled while Demon Spikes is active.$?s321299[Also increases your attack power by ${$321299s1}.1%.][]

description_blz.en_US: Increases Armor by 33.5% of your Agility. Armor bonus is doubled while Demon Spikes is active.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta la armadura una cantidad equivalente al 33.5% de tu agilidad. La bonificación de armadura se duplica mientras Pinchos demoníacos está activo.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta a Armadura em 33,5% da sua Agilidade. Bônus de Armadura dobrado quando os Espinhos Demoníacos estão ativos.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht die Rüstung um 33,5% Eurer Beweglichkeit. Der Rüstungsbonus wird verdoppelt, während 'Dämonenstachel' aktiv ist.
description_blz.en_GB: Increases Armor by 33.5% of your Agility. Armor bonus is doubled while Demon Spikes is active.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta la armadura un 33,5% de tu agilidad. El bonus de armadura se duplica mientras Púas de demonio está activa.
description_blz.fr_FR: Augmente le bonus d’Armure de Pointes démoniaques d’un montant égal à 33,5% de votre Agilité. Ce bonus est doublé tant que le sort Pointes démoniaques est actif.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta l'armatura del 33,5% della tua Agilità. Il bonus all'armatura raddoppia quando Aculei Demoniaci è attivo.
description_blz.ru_RU: Укрепляет броню на 33,5% вашей ловкости. Бонус к броне удваивается, пока действуют "Демонические шипы".
description_blz.ko_KR: 민첩성의 33.5%만큼 방어도가 증가합니다. 악마 쐐기가 활성화되어 있는 동안 방어도 보너스가 두 배로 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 護甲值提高等同於你敏捷的33.5%。惡魔尖刺作用期間，護甲值加成會加倍。
description_blz.zh_CN: 提高护甲值，相当于你敏捷值的33.5%。恶魔尖刺激活时，护甲值加成翻倍。
